Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE’s Investment Properties Team has been exclusively retained to offer for sale a free-standing, net lease BB’s Tex-Orleans (the “Property”) in San Antonio, Texas. BB’s is a cajun restaurant and New Orleans-themed café that currently operates ten locations in the Houston, Texas MSA and will be making their debut in the San Antonio market with this location. The Property is ideally positioned as an outparcel within Alamo Ranch Shopping Center, the premier shopping destination in far west San Antonio. BB’s is currently finalizing construction on their build-out and is expected to commence late summer 2021. They will be operating on a new 10-year lease term with minimal landlord responsibilities. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a dominant piece of real estate in San Antonio’s booming northwest corridor.
